(63, 1, 2, 62, 1, 8, 8, NULL, 'Connection of Truth and Sin', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of truth within believers. 2 John 1:2 speaks of truth dwelling in us, while 1 John 1:8 indicates that if truth is absent, we are deceived about our sinfulness.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
